    "body": "The possible values are `quorum`, `full`, `full-1`, or a number. This will control the minimum number of shards to recover from are required before an index can be recovered. For example, for an index with 2 replicas, `quorum` will require at least 2 shards to exists for each shard replication group.\n\nThe default is `quorum`.\n", 
